Meme with 4 Portraits of white man and some text.
Title: HOW "SELF-MADE" BILLIONAIRES GOT THEIR START 
image of Bill Gates: Mom sat on the same board as the CEO of IBM and convinced him to take a risk on her son's new company
image of Jeff Bezos: Started Amazon with 300,000 in seed capital from his parents and more from some rich friends
image of Warren Buffett: The son of a powerful congressmanwho owned an investment company 
image of Elon Musk: Dad owned an emerald mine in apartheid South Africa
